      "id": "tutorial-networking-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.424705,
      "replayEndSec": 13.591473,
      "narrationText": "第二步。让我们从命令行输入公网 IP、根域名、证书邮箱和 Cloudflare API 令牌。证书邮箱和令牌在你所有机器间共享，因此只需设置一次。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-01.63d8d7fa.mp3",
      "textHash": "63d8d7fa761cb80408691f8943963d4bbbfd1c87703770bfb07f7dc3fe91345a",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.725714,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-01-after.763c80fd.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.690612,
      "afterTextHash": "763c80fd2e42059f36032a5d05beab02bed78b616ebea2543f7b521a5f32e105"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 13.591473,
      "replayEndSec": 18.479059,
      "narrationText": "让我们确认基础设施配置已正确存储。公网 IP、根域名、证书邮箱，全都显示在配置中。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-02.e44e2fd5.mp3",
      "textHash": "e44e2fd5b05ee8bb3f02a32e95d4c4b776b2387f5f84b1306f17a0871c2823ac",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.672653,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-02-after.a3cb5b45.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.586122,
      "afterTextHash": "a3cb5b4553ff9e68259fe9763aeaf3963f1e598dc18e3b43f91e30e1d8c8b848"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 18.479059,
      "replayEndSec": 25.757057,
      "narrationText": "第三步。让我们将配置推送到服务器。这会自动在 Cloudflare 上创建 DNS 记录，并在机器上准备代理配置。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-03.c970aacf.mp3",
      "textHash": "c970aacfdabe986b10ecd5b545a161ec5b39a9e5726da0330f337e8b199f6b01",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.919184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-03-after.0ebb7b71.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.205714,
      "afterTextHash": "0ebb7b7161526f1e97efcc60e6a63973d44c9c9dbbae940b341c027e71a8f582"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 25.757057,
      "replayEndSec": 33.957312,
      "narrationText": "第四步开始。让我们创建一个名为 infra 的小仓库，代理将在这里运行，与应用仓库隔离。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-04.6d5c9a0f.mp3",
      "textHash": "6d5c9a0f1e2bb1f5ad75a777b9a36e2f8378ae2e4c6a768c2d82efdd27b920cf",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.810612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-04-after.54001b81.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.970612,
      "afterTextHash": "54001b8124b8ed173ffed507109fe4727d4616dbf81a1aae087d5bec30f40657"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 33.957312,
      "replayEndSec": 41.036573,
      "narrationText": "让我们应用内置的 proxy 模板。它包含 Traefik 以及 Let's Encrypt 和 Cloudflare DNS-01 验证的完整配置，开箱即用。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-05.c79903c0.mp3",
      "textHash": "c79903c06e796e5e4637026c590e5d6886fca95a9421aef1d6e1bc40405d2baa",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.44898,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-05-after.2530d999.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 1.410612,
      "afterTextHash": "2530d99991a4ec5d31471f8bc60f3ebec2baaea88685816e0708a1da8ce4fcab"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-networking-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 41.036573,
      "replayEndSec": 49.697921,
      "narrationText": "现在启动代理。Traefik 每五秒自动发现你的容器，TLS 证书由 Let's Encrypt 自动颁发。你的应用现在已经可以通过 HTTPS 在互联网上访问了。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-06.cba1c0b5.mp3",
      "textHash": "cba1c0b5d985a9e724c5377e4759eb1906a4134561249ab7d970487460ac3aef",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.355918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/tutorial-networking-06-after.2df17104.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.395918,
      "afterTextHash": "2df1710499dd3f2bcd3b7ed3063954c433696ed6b6487f19fc37c3563a873eee"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "150ec3948ecb93550d147d5d7789c7a58ff429499f5130ebb32624b68dcc6dc1",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/intro.150ec394.mp3",
      "narrationText": "好！让我们为你的应用配置一个真实域名，并自动启用 TLS。四个简短步骤，你就能登上互联网。",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.639184
    },
    {
      "id": "four-steps",
      "textHash": "3f5d01480485bf05a0312aa603945d4ef3c2df40a11a5aee099de7a5d468305d",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/four-steps.3f5d0148.mp3",
      "narrationText": "路径如下。拿到 Cloudflare API 令牌，在 CLI 上配置基础设施，推送到服务器，然后部署一个 Traefik 代理，由它替你处理 DNS 和证书。",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.490612
    },
    {
      "id": "open-cloudflare",
      "textHash": "435cb8c39c5d71310d5d8ccfbedf90a99a4f2a8fdaa18279286d1edd764b0c73",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-networking/open-cloudflare.435cb8c3.mp3",
      "narrationText": "首先，在浏览器中打开 Cloudflare 控制台。前往 My Profile，再到 API Tokens，创建一个具备 Zone DNS Edit 权限的令牌，让 CLI 能够管理你的 DNS 记录。",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.195918
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
